{"tid":2344132,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"飲啤酒食咩最正","createTime":"2020-12-28T12:53:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T20:41:36.000Z","uid":182683,"like":11,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"666833be0226d1325b79425df197155f647ea7a6","tid":2344132,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T12:53:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EEifwqa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEEifwqa.png&h=af0de452&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qwGMC5e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqwGMC5e.png&h=48c3095f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/weVUMYD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FweVUMYD.png&h=7690f5ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國野黎 餸啤酒一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n金色係連埋肥膏一齊炸 太肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我食左幾舊都唔係好掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以推薦粉紅色個包 冇肥膏版本<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />飲緊酒好快成包食哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2包都好脆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係鬼佬個種硬硬地既脆 總之飲酒食爽呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n味道：7/10 <br />\n極邪惡咩咩咩 <br />\n<br />\nIg有片有興趣可以睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nIg:<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hkfoodghost/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhkfoodghost%2F&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9UzxxphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=f8a5a347\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hkfoodghost/</a><br />\n<br />\n食譜就呢到：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtube.com/channel/UCqRF5PLGsAWPGjluK1DoBNw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCqRF5PLGsAWPGjluK1DoBNw&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9UzxxphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=bcd1f45d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtube.com/channel/UCqRF5PLGsAWPGjluK1DoBNw</a>"},{"pid":"a3c4db6d1e3503933bd51f46dc172fd99a65f9cc","tid":2344132,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T12:54:08.000Z","msg":"食台妹最正<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66455b04301b4ab5d5c0fdd01f301694c8daa7fb","tid":2344132,"uid":365166,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T12:56:21.000Z","msg":"台妹最正<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8049d9d79ea2c490e03d6853664e2a8bd73c0142","tid":2344132,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3c4db6d1e3503933bd51f46dc172fd99a65f9cc","tid":2344132,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T12:54:08.000Z","msg":"食台妹最正<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T13:00:21.000Z","msg":"我唔想變木耳 唔好入黎留台妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab7f7b6e3e5c4acf1ed091776a68bc50523c0e03","tid":2344132,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T13:04:46.000Z","msg":"雞"},{"pid":"4ab4f874d6e258493643d564fd05ce84a94d157e","tid":2344132,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8049d9d79ea2c490e03d6853664e2a8bd73c0142","tid":2344132,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3c4db6d1e3503933bd51f46dc172fd99a65f9cc","tid":2344132,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T12:54:08.000Z","msg":"食台妹最正<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T13:00:21.000Z","msg":"我唔想變木耳 唔好入黎留台妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T13:13:17.000Z","msg":"食手指<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\